---
description: Cairn ground-state awareness — decisions, invariants, and active tasks
alwaysApply: true
---

This project uses Cairn for ground-state management. If `.cairn/` exists at
the repo root:

- Never invent architectural patterns; check `cairn_in_scope({path_globs})`
  before making structural changes.
- Before UI work, call `cairn_components_in_scope({path_globs})` — USE
  existing components before EXTENDING, EXTEND before CREATE.
- Record non-obvious choices with `cairn_record_decision`.
- Use the `cairn-direction` skill for any code-change task to get a tightened
  spec before implementing.
